  ('a294114b-e81b-4297-9343-08ca9d8339a1','98eb2017-36d5-4d31-bcd2-37ff9e3c8ebb',70.0,'Owner age est ~60 (age inferred from tenure), tenure 59yr (+4).',70.0,'Service mix=tax_bookkeeping (59yr recurring book, 4-partner multi).',68.0,'3 tells: 59-yr firm, multi-generational client relationships; Partner Emeritus J. Raymond Strauch Jr. => active succession transition; ''Smaller established firm'' self-description => not aggressive growth.',81.0,'Hot vertical (Citrin Cooperman/Aprio/Schellman/CBIZ TX expansion); major metro San Antonio+3.',71.0,'B_forward','59-yr San Antonio CPA. Owner est ~?yr. Tells: 3. B-tier solid forward.','Move from compliance-only to advisory bundle (CFO/advisory/payroll), digital portal (Canopy/Liscio), 12-15% rate lift. Double EBITDA margin from ~25% to 40-45% over 24 months.','medium',0.7),
  ('212e0905-3f01-4110-b4e1-c0f101e631d4','98eb2017-36d5-4d31-bcd2-37ff9e3c8ebb',96.0,'Owner age est ~70 (src: founder_1981_proxy + multi-credential_career => born ~1955-60), tenure 45yr (+4).',80.0,'Service mix=full_service (45yr recurring book, 3-partner multi).',35.0,'OVERRIDE: Family succession father->daughter (Pamela Rodriguez Reiffert) in place.',81.0,'Hot vertical (Citrin Cooperman/Aprio/Schellman/CBIZ TX expansion); major metro San Antonio+3.',71.0,'B_forward','45-yr San Antonio CPA. Owner est ~70yr. Tells: 3. B-tier solid forward.','Add cloud advisory + virtual CFO services (Botkeeper/Canopy/Liscio), automate compliance, raise rates 10-15%. EBITDA uplift 300-500bps + recurring-revenue mix shift.','medium',0.7),
